             was indicted for <rs id="t18270531-97-off486" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270531-97-off486" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270531-97-off486" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270531-97-cd487" type="crimeDate">17th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270531-97-off486 t18270531-97-cd487"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 4s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18270531-97-victim646" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Graham
                     <interp inst="t18270531-97-victim646" type="surname" value="Graham"></interp>
